#

Fluffy Buttermilk Waffles

25 min
$8.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyGlutenEggs

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastBrunchEasyComfort Food

Description

Light, airy, and buttery waffles that are perfect for breakfast or brunch!

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 2 cups
  • buttermilk: 1 3/4 cups
  • eggs: 2
  • baking powder: 2 tablespoons
  • sugar: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1/2 teaspoon
  • unsalted butter: 1/2 cup
  • vanilla extract: 1 teaspoon
